=== MACPORTS PACKAGE ===

NB: Working in progress


- INDEX PORTFILE
sudo echo "file:///{path/to/your/svn/ntopng/directory}packages/macports/ports" >> /opt/local/etc/macports/sources.conf   
cd {path/to/your/svn/ntopng/directory}packages/macports/ports"
portindex


- INSTALL PORTS
#Stable version of ntopng
sudo port info ntopng
sudo port install ntopng
#Svn version of ntopng
sudo port info ntopng-devel
sudo port install ntopng-devel